ebsite=[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827075037/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-feature/2016/08/13/feature-rezero-director-and-composer-discuss-who-the-true-heroine-is-emilia-or-rem |accessdate=2016-08-18 |archivedate=2016-08-27 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，
也因此導致其相關產品如抱枕需求量過大而延遲發售<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2016/07/31-1/rezero-rem-pillow-delayed-due-to-unanticipated-demand |title="Re:Zero" Rem Pillow Delayed Due To Unanticipated Demand |last=Green |first=Scott |date=2016-07-31 |website=[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]] |accessdate=2016-07-31 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801154936/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2016/07/31-1/rezero-rem-pillow-delayed-due-to-unanticipated-demand |archivedate=2016-08-01 }}</ref>，官方甚至推出了等身大的雷姆[[手辦|手辦]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nlab.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1612/23/news046.html |script-title=ja:「Re:ゼロ」のレムが等身大フィギュアに　お値段148万円 |date=2016-12-23 |website=itmedia.co.jp |accessdate=2017-07-08 |language=ja |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630001311/http://nlab.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1612/23/news046.html |archivedate=2017-06-30 }}</ref>。
